      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions replicated in simulation within stated uncertainty bands; fluid temperature and hematocrit controlled.",
      "rationale": "Flow rate and rotational speed are matched; however hematocrit variation across test runs was not controlled and inlet turbulence intensity was estimated rather than measured."
