      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative metric (e.g., E_rel) with uncertainty bounds for hemolysis index and pressure rise across all operating points.",
      "rationale": "Qualitative agreement reported for pressure-flow curves; hemolysis index absolute error exceeds 30% at two of five operating points and no formal validation metric with uncertainty bounds is provided."
